This patch applies variant pricing v2 changes to PricingStep.tsx

To apply in contractnest-ui directory:
  cd contractnest-ui
  git apply ../MANUAL_COPY_FILES/r4-c2c-variant-pricing/PricingStep.patch

Changes:
1. Import TreePine icon and SelectedVariant type (already done in v1)
2. Replace simple variantPrices init with empty object
3. Add handleApplyToAll callback (copies base price to all variants)
4. Replace simple variant rows with full variant pricing section:
   - Shows base price from primary pricing record
   - "Apply ₹X to All" button
   - Tax context banner
   - Per-variant price input with currency symbol
   - Override highlight on modified variants
